        <div class="container">
            <p>Â© 2025 SEOtools.site â€” All Rights Reserved</p>
            <p style="margin-top: 10px; font-size: 0.9rem;">Accurate Age Calculator â€¢ 100% Free â€¢ Private & Secure</p>
